<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ أَجْرِ الْمَرْأَةِ إِذَا تَصَدَّقَتْ أَوْ أَطْعَمَتْ مِنْ بَيْتِ زَوْجِهَا غَيْرَ مُفْسِدَةٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤٣٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">وَالْأَعْمَشُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">أَبِي وَائِلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6088">مَسْرُوقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span>، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>،<span class="c5"> تَعْنِي:</span> إِذَا تَصَدَّقَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ مِنْ بَيْتِ زَوْجِهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>